For example, I have UI with two tabs and pages.

The first one contains form with combo box. This combo box has got binding for selected value.
When I navigate to the second page and go back and after that I change combo box value then Selected value setter will be called twice: first with selected value, second time with null value:

P.S.: I'm using GalaSoft light mvvm framework

        public KeyValueModel SelectedValue
